{"tid":2148760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"壹傳媒工會：警翻閲記者文件 超手令範圍侵犯新聞自由","createTime":"2020-08-10T05:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T16:22:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":258,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb4f976454e158f8f8661d506b337c9f8e48d51","tid":2148760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F126565&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=4c366131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126565</a><br />\n<br />\n警方繼續封鎖壹傳媒集團將軍澳總部調查。壹傳媒工會發言人林偉聰表示，有警員曾經翻閲記者文件，做法侵犯新聞自由。林偉聰表示，早上傳出多名高層被捕的消息後，超過200名警員和多輛警車很快就包圍集團大樓，由於疫情關係，很多職員在家工作，並非太多人在公司，他透過《蘋果日報》直播收看警方行動。林偉聰引述警方國安處高級警司李桂華表示，行動並非檢取新聞材料，但他說，多名警員曾經肆意翻閲記者桌上的文件資料，明顯侵犯報社的法律權益，以及超越手令權力範圍，嚴重侵犯新聞自由，在場的總編輯多次要求查閱警方手令內容，亦被拒絕。林偉聰又說，如果警方只是搜查幾名高層的辦公室，為何動用數百警力重重包圍大樓，他質疑當局和警方企圖向報社施壓，相信員工會繼續緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-10 13:26:26"},{"pid":"fd8eba50a225626db48b4fb1a2c62b6769ace8a7","tid":2148760,"uid":354682,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話想去server房"},{"pid":"2df3d1b79d1bfd661b543949d1c3b0ef8939dd38","tid":2148760,"uid":363427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ebbd652a91f55ff9ac49ac8a10115b6fe0c91f","tid":2148760,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\