:26:26"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"現場班狗心諗「終於可以破壞新聞自由，Yeah！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"終於?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"攞正牌破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW用國安法算唔算攞正牌"},{"pid":"7bb1fde17ee7b8b9600a1f9db6dbac3dc55a0a6f","tid":2148760,"uid":333470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a36579e11d696d26a1c208b250fded178e5febe3","tid":2148760,"uid":136661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"搜查令唔俾被搜查嘅人睇，佢點知嗰張野係咩同埋有冇效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"屌佢老尾之前試過搜完再向法庭申請後補都得 香港法治笑話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74053ff0a5d73c6f2fcb6c99e8e6767a1df68b38","tid":2148760,"uid":78333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c217dacaafe3899b6e204693ea753bd3d74a43","tid":2148760,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8c8045c5277ff78c6214d4f1a96dd123d30627","tid":2148760,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"一來係支共趁機攞料，二來D前線狗發洩"},{"pid":"b32bb84f5481890f94206ecf33ebfceb01858bd0","tid":2148760,"uid":37193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"似係查蘋果有咩料仲未爆 跟手依家攞料作定故仔？"},{"pid":"212985869b332623531a55d1d3f4835392e9e9b0","tid":2148760,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd8eba50a225626db48b4fb1a2c62b6769ace8a7","tid":2148760,"uid"